Your recursive function seems to be calculating the sum of all integers from 1 to n. However, there is a small mistake in the base case. When n equals 1000, the function should return 1000, not when n equals 1000. Here's the corrected code:

public static long s(int n) {
    if (n == 1000) {
        return 1000;
    } else if (n > 1000) {
        return 0;
    } else {
        return s(n + 1) + n;
    }
}

